flowchart TD
    A[PCG Module 10\nGenerate candidate Seed s] --> B[Lookup attached\nSeed-Ritual R]
    B --> C[Load SeedContractV1\nΔm_seed and invariants]
    C --> D[Read current metrics\nm_cur from resurrection spine]
    D --> E[Project metrics\nm_proj = f(m_cur, Δm_seed, c\])]
    E --> F{All m_proj >=\nR.min_entertainment_bands?}
    F -- no --> F1[Reject seed s\n(reason: floor violation)]
    F1 --> Z[Return: do_not_register]

    F -- yes --> G[Check DET budget\nC_DET + w_s·ΔDET(s) <= B_DET^R?]
    G -- no --> G1[Reject seed s\n(reason: DET over budget)]
    G1 --> Z

    G -- yes --> H[Resolve gore styles\nallowed_style_refs]
    H --> I[Filter styles by GXI\nand consent tier]
    I --> J{Any style s* with\nA(s*) = 1?}
    J -- no --> J1[Reject seed s\n(reason: no admissible style)]
    J1 --> Z

    J -- yes --> K[Bind Seed s to\nSeed-Ritual R\nand style subset]
    K --> L[Register Seed s\ninto registry]

    %% Runtime branch
    L --> R0[Runtime helper\nH.should_trigger_sequence]
    R0 --> R1[Read active ritual R\nand player state]
    R1 --> R2[Recompute m_proj,\nupdate E_DET, enforce floors]
    R2 --> R3{Floors and DET\nbudget satisfied?}
    R3 -- no --> R4[Return false\n(do not fire)]
    R4 --> Z2[Runtime: candidate discarded]

    R3 -- yes --> R5[Evaluate stage\nmin_intensity_envelope]
    R5 --> R6[Clamp Director's AV\nplan to ritual floors]
    R6 --> R7[Trigger Seed s\nwith bound styles]
    R7 --> Z3[Runtime: fired\nand logged]
